text:
4 saal mein Divyanshu kab bola tha tujhe, yaad nahi aa raha yaar, Barot. Jab tu pehli baar orientation ke time pe room mein mila tha, mujhe laga tha, kaafi chill aur independent insaan hai, mazza aayega kaafi.

LEKIN!!!
Saari bakchodiyaan bhi tujhse hi seekhi hai, for a short period of time :), phir toh mein baap ban gaya tha. Saari harkate wing mein saath hi kari hai bhai. Mess mein baithke tujhe saari aaptijanak chizzein khaate dekhna, shayad hi bhul paaunga mein. Jahaan bhi nashe hote the, vahaan aap sadaiv milte the, aur aqsar, aap hi ki wajah se nashe ho rahe hote the. 
YO BRO YO BRO
Ab soch ke lagta hai, tu nahi hota hamesha irritate karne ke liye, toh kaafi boring ho jaata sab. Cooler churaana, cooler ke aage pade rehna. AUR AAPKI NUDES!!! I am sure supermodels ko pachhar sakte hai aap, ek jhatke mein. 
Aise toh yeh likhna kabhi khatam hi nahi kar paaunga mein, itna kuch hai likhne ko.
Har bakchodi mein aap saath the. Trips, parties, bullas, nightouts, and tera zor zor se hasna.

MOTTU, ab toh aap JAVA Developer ban gaye hai, bina Java sikhe, I hope bhulenge nahi aap. 
Mein toh nahi bhulunga tujhe, 1100 jo lene bache hai tujhse xD

Until next time,

author: Ayush  Jain

text:
Tere baare mein soch ke hi mann mein apshabdo ki leher daudti hai :)
Ritambhara as an experience would have been incomplete without you. Harkate hi aisi hai teri. Starting mein tu pelke fraud maara (sabne hi maara tha vaise xD), lekin gaali sirf tujhe hi padti thi XD
I wouldn't be exaggerating if teri bloodlust ho gayi thi core team ko toh. Humaara Eid ka chaand - Harshit Rao.
Lekin, jabse tameez se kaam karna shuru kiya, tab toh kya hi kehne, aag hi laga di. Aur tabse leke, Ritambhara Finals tak, bahut MAZZE kiye hai saath mein!!   MAZZA HI AA GAYA MATLAB!
Mess mein bakchodi, galti se hall mein dikh gaye tab bakchodi, apni doobi hui marketing ko bachaane ki local trips pe bakchodi. Secys ki g**nd fatt ti thi bhai tujhse. Swag hi alag hai tera.

Agar apan dono ka bas chalta, toh Ritambhara treat ke paise toh bachch hi jaate nahi? Lekin, it was an experience. I was high, Ritika was shy, and bachcho se bakchodi karaane ka onus tune sambhaaala.
But, there's another side of you apart from this bakchod one, the serious attitude towards your UPSC prep. And it really fascinates me, and I kinda admire it. 
APAN TEENO se better koi team ho nahi sakti thi Ritambhara chaapne ke liye, everyone was perfect for it, in their own ways.

IAS banke, Krishna se contact zaroor kario, unke kaafi saare personal agendas hai XD
BEST OF LUCK BINCH!
Ek trip bachchi hai abhi AKHR ki, tab milte hai :)

Until next time,
Your Co-Manager,
Ritambhara'19 <3
